introduction: The video discusses the virtual conference, which is happening on February 15th and 22nd, featuring AI experts and product owners from various companies such as Uber, LinkedIn, and Netflix. The conference also includes AI product owner and engineering tracks, as well as hands-on workshops. The video highlights the importance of benchmarking and evaluation in the AI field, with a focus on LM evals and its role in production.
